Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That ain't a giraffe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a long neck,\Nbut it's a horse. A long-horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...I cut a bamboo tree and a spirit appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Foxy Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty! All we want... is a showdown!
