Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my house! I'm in your debt!\NLet me offer you some hospitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right! Food!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see my house again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's custom in this village to treat\Nvisitors to milk from our farm animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Village? Where's the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And your farm animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "where"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The village is gone! And the farm animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real. Villages don't just\Ndisappear in ten years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can explain it later.\NFor now, let me treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I had some milk stored away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stored away? You realize you were\Non those stilts for ten years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully this cheese is to your liking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look away! That's obviously\Nyour ten-year-old milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make yourselves at home then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This cheese is edible, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! It's only ten-year-old cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you folks, I live a\Nlaid-back life on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made my stomach different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, now. Whippersnappers\Nthese days are so frail...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Call... a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're funny, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nomads?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're carefree nomads,\Nalways on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how your village\Ndisappeared after only ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the island of\NLong Ring Long Land. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's technically a single ring-shaped island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of the sea, it's usually\Ndivided into ten separate islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But on one day a year,\Nthe tide gets especially low,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and for those few hours, the island\Nregains its true, singular form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We use this fact to migrate from one\Nisland to the next every three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got left behind \Nafter the village moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, old guy! You're a big dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If they stay on each island for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then it'd take 'em thirty years\Nto come all the way back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking away the time you\Nwere stuck on those stilts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't see them again\Nfor about twenty more years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I only I had a hooorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could catch up to the others in five years
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,by crossing to a new \Nisland once every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hooorse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The most beautiful\Nanimals on these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They gallop through the\Ngrassy plains so gracefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're absolutely necessary\Nto migrate from island to island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong and can carry large loads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't migrate on foot, either--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the tide would come back in before\NI even got across to the next island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just take a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know how to sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if we charged a Log Pose here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't point to the \Nnext island in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All ten islands are actually\None big island, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just wait here twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? It'll be lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a "hooorse" a "horse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! A horse! We saw one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Shelly! You waited for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shelly! You're so adorable!\NThis sure brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so long since I last saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've been so lonely,\Nall by yourself all those years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to ride on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that horse was waiting\Nfor him the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She must really like him a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that horse sure is \Nfast! I wanna ride too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is graceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly. Let's cross the sea\Ntogether on the next low tide day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All those days with rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All those days with snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting through it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly... Do you really insist\Non waiting for Tonjit-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take all \Nyour friends with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Littonto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be back here for 27 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have no idea where Tonjit-san even is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my advice, come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stay too! I'm gonna\Nwait for Grandpa with Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not! You can't \Nstay here all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa's here! I know it!\NI'm gonna wait for him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Live well, Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm afraid of heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--You okay?!\N--We heard a gunshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--Just a sec!\N--Old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The horse is mine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah! That horse is our boss's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you don't know this face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know your face! I'm gonna beat it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They don't know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Boss! Don't get depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying! I bet he's just saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't possibly know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing, Hamburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Foxy! I take whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this be a lesson, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so worked up\Nabout a single horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunting is nothing more than entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we know who you are!\NWe've done our homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, with a\N100-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro, with a 60-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A total bounty of 160 million\Nwith only seven people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We Foxy Pirates challenge you\NStraw Hats to a "Davy Back Fight"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking crazy! Just bring it on!\NIf you wanna fight, let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy... A Davy Back fight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That explains the ship\Nwe encountered near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--Which way do we turn?!\N--How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Someone, give orders! Navigator!\N--Don't got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Captain!\N--Don't got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Luffy! That game...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! We'll lose crew members!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, don't agree to his game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! I heard you say it, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly agreed to my challenge just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he, Porche-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Boss! I heard him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think you can back out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, what? You're not man\Nenough to keep your word?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't get talked into it!\N--But... the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly... Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself! You hit your back hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--You two! Step aside!\N--Old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shelly faithfully waited ten\Nyears for me! How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, old guy! They're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Davy Back Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.19,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Unruly"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The fight begins the\Nmoment two captains are in agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As we speak, our captain\Nis challenging your captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenging? What kind of\Nsleepy nonsense is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want a fight, just start one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've never heard of a Davy Back Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fight. It's a pirate game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A game that supposedly arose\Nlong ago on "Pirate Island,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which is said to be a pirate\Nparadise somewhere in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In it, pirates plunder each other\Nfor top-notch crew members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pirates plunder each other?!\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you've survived this\Nlong without even knowing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Davy Back Fight is about\Nswiping crew members!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After each match, the winner can take
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,any crew member they want\Nfrom the opposing team!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's chosen must immediately\Nswear loyalty to their new captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Davy Jones,\Nthe pirate of the deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you lose... you lose a crew member?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, if the enemy ship\Nhas no one of interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they can instead be stripped of their\NJolly Roger-- the life of their ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So crewmates and pride are on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning will make you stronger,\Nwhile losing will mean a serious loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a vicious game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean\Nthat ship we ran across earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without an organized crew,\Nsails, or even a captain was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you run into the\NFang-Frog Pirates' ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They fell prey to our game earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to our new crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Long live the Foxy Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the former captain of that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Former ship doctor!\N--Former navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Former shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried five three-coin \Ngames, but lost 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourteen men and our flag, \Ntaken just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With so many people jumping ship like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it was more like a merger than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots. How can you be so happy,\Nditching your crew like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. The ship's in \Na watery grave by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Watery grave...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no talking reason with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd never agree to such a\Nridiculous game in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! A regular crew member\Ncan't make that decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This game only begins when\Ntwo captains reach an agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, you're all in this game\Nif your captain nods his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unwritten rule \Nin the pirate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, and we'll be completely humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if we're humiliated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than live in shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it. This is how men are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgh! I gotta stop Luffy, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother. It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The captains will signal \Nthe start of the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,by firing shots at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit here and--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He agreed to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's agreed to the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You idiot! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you agree to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how horrific this game is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we just won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our challenge is now officially accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will too, Split-Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,--Split-Head...?\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?! Our boss is a sensitive man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a heart of glass.\NDoesn't suit him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I told you not to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about the horse and the\Nold guy makes me mad too, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that anger to thrash 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He got back up way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to teach you a thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankfurters! Get your frankfurters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rum and cheese! Crackers and salted meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got yakisoba noodles too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the opening ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Please quiet down! Please quiet down!\N--Shut up! You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--C'mon! Let's hear the odds!\N--All participants, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is looking fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all Split-Head's crew members?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! There's so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Five jumbo yakisobas, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:09.80,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Cotton Candy" "Yakisoba Noodles"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, men! Simmer down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Porche-chan!\N--Sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the pledge to follow\Nthese three rules about losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the only way to take back crewmates,\NJolly Rogers, or anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is through another Davy Back Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, anyone taken by the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,must swear loyalty to that\Nship's captain immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Third, if your Jolly Roger is taken,\Nyou can't ever display it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san! I bought some cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you guys be so calm about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still moping about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you break these rules,\Nyou'll be considered dishonorable pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and sent to Davy Jones' Locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you swear to uphold them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--I swear!\N--I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Straw Hat! I'll let you choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One coin? Two coins? Or three coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose whichever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Boss! You're so gracious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the number of games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our boss is letting you choose\Nif it should be a one-match game
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or all the way up to a three-match game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The game'll be more fun with more stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--So I'll go with...\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Three coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Why'd you add them?!\NAnd include an enemy in the count?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So many morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby announce this three-coin,\Northodox-rules game...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...to Davy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Davy Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An old pirate cursed by the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who's said to live in the depths\Nof the sea to this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives at the bottom of the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the legend says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the ships and treasures \Nthat sink into the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,are said to go to his ship's bosun--\Nhis "locker," in other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the sea is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
